
rhtml extracts text and layout from HTML documents, using xulrunner.

version 0.4 (2010-04-13)

---------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION
---------------------------------------------------------------------

rhtml requires Mozilla xulrunner and Xvfb, which should be part of
your Linux distro. If these are not at /usr/bin/xulrunner and
/usr/bin/xvfb-run, adjust the paths at the top of the rhtml file.

Not try calling

rhtml test/simple.html

---------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
---------------------------------------------------------------------

rhtml [-d int] file.html

 -d int : debug level

